1. *Stali* smo na semaforu. (*We stopped* at the traffic light.)
2. Videli smo da su *stali* radovi na gradilištu. (We saw that the construction works *stopped*.)
3. Kada smo *stigli* na stanicu, voz već nije *stajao* tamo. (When we *arrived* at the station, the train was no longer *stopping* there.)
4. Zamolila sam ih da *stanu* sa radom dok ne rešimo problem. (I asked them to *stop* working until we solve the problem.)
5. Kada su *ustali* sa stolica, primetila sam da su umorni. (When they *got up* from the chairs, I noticed that they were tired.)
6. Nadam se da će nam *stajati* ova nova mašina još mnogo godina. (I hope that this new machine will *last* us many years.)
7. U žurbi sam *prestala* da *stavljam* šminku na pola puta. (I *stopped* putting on makeup halfway in a hurry.)
8. *Nastavili* smo sa poslom nakon pauze za ručak. (We *resumed* working after lunch break.)